      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The double-VANOS system is fully serviced, ensuring optimal cam timing across the entire rev range. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is exceptional, featuring documented rear subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry tuned for maximum lateral grip. Finished in concours-level Carbon Black, this vehicle shows zero signs of mechanical fatigue or cosmetic wear, boasting factory-spec compression and a pristine undercarriage.",
